- Script excludes common development directories
- Shows hierarchical view of project directories
- Made executable for easy access

## Current Status
- Fixed HandlerTest to use Container instead of Application
- Updated IngestNamesCommandTest to use proper temporary file handling
- Updated SuggesterServiceIntegrationTest with correct namespace and property names
- Updated SuggesterControllerTest with proper mocking and assertions
- Fixed namespace issues in SuggesterController
- Fixed MockSolrClient to handle nicknames and case sensitivity properly
- Improved fuzzy matching with increased distance and proper parameter handling
- Fixed parameter mapping in SuggesterController
- Standardized response format to use sequential arrays
- Fixed ServiceProvidersTest to use proper Application instance
- Improved query precision with stricter fuzzy matching and boosting
- Removed result limit to show all relevant matches
- Added proper logging configuration
- Added score logging and detailed error reporting
- Included scores in API responses
- Refactored SuggesterService to follow SOLID principles

